My suggestion: Hire more responsible workers and clean up your resturants more often, please. You'll be better off with my suggestion.

For a combined Popeye's/Burger King spot, I was pleasantly surprised to find the food delicious, fresh, and well prepared. I presented 3 coupons for my large order at the BK section, and all was handled wonderfully by the staff. Items were all labeled correctly (bacon, double pattied, grilled) and I received plenty of condiments and utensils. All food items were accounted for, and it all tasted great. The manager is a true gentleman, as well. I actually lost my kid's iPad in the parking lot on the way out at night, and he reached out the very next day for us to retrieve it. We were so grateful. The service was already fantastic, and this just topped it all in a fantastic way. Recommended!
